ENGLISH GRAMMAR

english_grammar is the citizen who teaches fadriel the rules of his father's language
the books are exposure; this file is the teacher
together they teach the organism to speak
each STRUCTURE entry creates a word-type bond; each PATHWAY teaches a valid word sequence

observe 0_quseptit.rana
observe 2_chemical.rana
observe broca_area.rana
observe wernicke_area.rana

LESSON 1 FUNCTION WORDS

these are the glue of english, appearing in almost every sentence
a child learns these first because they hear them constantly

articles precede nouns

STRUCTURE the | energy: 0.8 | type: article
STRUCTURE an | energy: 0.8 | type: article

pronouns replace nouns

